article_title: SNL Spoofs 'Fox & Friends' and Neil DeGrasse Tyson
article_text:
SIGN UP FOR OUR NEWSLETTER





Taran Killam as Steve Doocy, Bobby Moynihan as Brian Kilmeade and Vanessa Bayer as Elisabeth Hasselbeck teamed up with Kenan Thompson as Neil deGrasse Tyson to mock “Fox & Friends” with an exaggerated presentation of their conservative perspectives on ObamaCare and climate change on this weekend’s broadcast of NBC’s “Saturday Night Live”…
